<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>A Chapter Closing</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg1: #07070b;
      --bg2: #10111a;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --card-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      --text: #f4f1ec;
      --muted: rgba(244,241,236,0.72);
      --gold: #d8b26e;
      --rose: #c56b7b;
      --violet: #8b6cff;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --shadow: 0 25px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    }* { box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  color: var(--text);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(216,178,110,0.12), transparent 30%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(197,107,123,0.15), transparent 25%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 10%, rgba(139,108,255,0.12), transparent 25%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg1), var(--bg2));
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

.noise {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.06;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 42px 42px;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 55%, transparent 100%);
}

.wrap {
  width: min(980px, calc(100% - 32px));
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 38px 0 60px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.hero {
  padding: 40px 28px 28px;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 28px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: -120px -40px auto auto;
  width: 260px;
  height: 260px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(216,178,110,0.20), transparent 70%);
  filter: blur(10px);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.kicker {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(216,178,110,0.35);
  border-radius: 999px;
  color: #f9e6c0;
  background: rgba(216,178,110,0.10);
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.kicker .dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold);
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--gold);
}

h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);
  line-height: 1.02;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
}

.subtitle {
  margin: 16px 0 0;
  color: var(--muted);
  max-width: 720px;
  font-size: 1.06rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 0.9fr;
  gap: 22px;
  margin-top: 22px;
}

.panel {
  padding: 26px;
  border-radius: 24px;
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

.panel h2 {
  margin: 0 0 14px;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2px;
}

.panel p {
  margin: 0 0 16px;
  color: rgba(244,241,236,0.88);
  line-height: 1.9;
  font-size: 1.02rem;
}

.quote {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  padding: 18px 18px 18px 20px;
  background: rgba(216,178,110,0.07);
  border-radius: 16px;
  margin: 18px 0;
  color: #fff5e0;
}

.timeline {
  display: grid;
  gap: 14px;
}

.step {
  padding: 16px 18px;
  border-radius: 18px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}

.step strong {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  color: #ffe6be;
}

.closing {
  margin-top: 22px;
  padding: 28px;
  border-radius: 26px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(197,107,123,0.35);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(197,107,123,0.14), rgba(139,108,255,0.10), rgba(216,178,110,0.10));
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.closing::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: auto -80px -90px auto;
  width: 220px;
  height: 220px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(197,107,123,0.22), transparent 68%);
  filter: blur(12px);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.closing h3 {
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3vw, 2rem);
}

.closing p {
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
}

.signature {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 18px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.4px;
  transition: transform 0.28s ease, background 0.28s ease, color 0.28s ease, box-shadow 0.28s ease;
  cursor: default;
  user-select: none;
}

.signature:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,178,110,0.24), rgba(197,107,123,0.22), rgba(139,108,255,0.18));
  color: #fff8ec;
  box-shadow: 0 12px 34px rgba(216,178,110,0.18);
}

.footer-note {
  margin-top: 16px;
  color: rgba(244,241,236,0.6);
  font-size: 0.93rem;
}

.fade-up {
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease both;
}

.fade-up.delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.12s; }
.fade-up.delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.24s; }
.fade-up.delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.36s; }
.fade-up.delay-4 { animation-delay: 0.48s; }

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero, .panel, .closing { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
}

@media (max-width: 540px) {
  .wrap { width: min(100% - 20px, 980px); padding-top: 18px; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.1rem; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 0.98rem; }
}
.final-btn {
  margin-top: 18px;
  padding: 12px 22px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,178,110,0.25), rgba(197,107,123,0.25));
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.final-btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,178,110,0.5), rgba(197,107,123,0.5));
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(216,178,110,0.2);
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="noise"></div>  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="hero fade-up">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="dot"></span> An emotional closing page</div>
      <h1>When a bond stops feeling mutual.</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        This page carries the truth, the silence, the effort, and the final acceptance.
        It is written like a closure letter — soft, honest, and unforgettable.
      </p>
    </section><section class="grid">
  <article class="panel fade-up delay-1">
    <h2>The message</h2>
    <p>
      I trusted you.
    </p>
    <p>
      Not casually… not normally. I trusted you in a way where you slowly became a part of my life —
      and then without realising it, you became the centre of it.
    </p>
    <p>
      And maybe that is exactly where I went wrong.
    </p>
    <p>
      Because while I was getting closer, I could feel you going the opposite way.
    </p>
    <div class="quote">
      I noticed your texts. The dryness. The distance. The lack of effort.
    </div>
    <p>
      The things I did for you — the edits, the website, the time I invested — they were never for a “thank you”.
      They were my way of building something real.
    </p>
    <p>
      But your replies, your behaviour, your consistency kept telling me one thing again and again:
      this bond does not exist for you the way it does for me.
    </p>
  </article>

  <aside class="panel fade-up delay-2">
    <h2>What I felt</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="step">
        <strong>5 days of silence</strong>
        I stopped myself again and again, fighting the urge to just talk normally.
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <strong>Deep attachment</strong>
        This was never casual for me. I was emotionally invested in a way that was hard to hide.
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <strong>One-sided effort</strong>
        I was the one initiating, holding, trying, and carrying the bond forward.
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <strong>Final understanding</strong>
        One-sided effort, no matter how pure, still ends up nowhere.
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</section>

<section class="panel fade-up delay-3" style="margin-top:22px;">
  <h2>Acceptance</h2>
  <p>
    You will never know how difficult these last 5 days were for me. Not texting you. Holding back.
    Keeping myself from reaching out again and again.
  </p>
  <p>
    I saw the pattern clearly: I was the one putting in effort while you kept everything limited.
    Even when I shared things that mattered to me, your responses felt empty.
  </p>
  <p>
    Maybe I gave more than what you were ever meant to receive.
    And I know this clearly — it is going to take me time to forget this, to detach from you,
    because what I felt was real.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="closing fade-up delay-4">
  <h3>Now finally, our chapter is closing.</h3>
  <p>
    Take care, and thank you for all your memories.
  </p>
  <p style="margin-top:12px; opacity:0.95;">
    <em>Singing off with this — Swayam Mishra.</em>
  </p>
  <div class="signature">— Swayam Mishra</div> <button class="final-btn" onclick="handleClosure()">
  Close This Chapter
</button>
  <div class="footer-note">Hover over the signature to reveal the highlighted finish.</div>
</section>

  </main>
</body>
</html>
